      <title>欧盟对苹果、谷歌、Meta 进行新数字法测试调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟对苹果公司、Alphabet公司旗下谷歌和Meta Platforms公司是否遵守限制大型科技公司权力的严格新法律展开全面调查，它们面临着潜在巨额罚款的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
